opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 25th day of July, 2012 the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is hereby DENIED.
The Commonwealth’s Motion to Supplement the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is hereby DENIED AS MOOT.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
